                    <p>EnsiasCareer is a place where ensiastes and companies can finally meet and have a direct communication. With a simple search you will find different recommendations, whether you are a student who is looking for his internship, or a company who is searching for potential profiles amongst ensiastes. Sign up to discover more.</p>
                    <h2>ARE YOU AN ENSIASTE ?</h2>
                    <p>Are you struggling to find an internship offer that suits you, are you scared of jumping into an internship that you know little about. EnsiasCareer gives you the chance to not only search for a convenient offer according to your criteria, but to also compare, see other people's experience and even post your own experience. EnsiasCareer is your guide to find the perfect opportunity. </p>
                    <h2>ARE YOU A COMPANY ?</h2>
                    <p>EnsiasCareer is your gate to post your internship offers directly to ENSIAS students. And therefore to ensure an online presence, and to be in touch with ensiastes. It also enables you to find potential profiles that you might be interested in. With a click you will get a list of students according to your specific criteria. Get started and post your first offer. </p>
